@lisa_blackmore Dr Lisa,
we understand your considerations and dissatisfaction, but, please, rest assured that we are making every effort to locate your luggage as soon as possible.
Once again, we thank you for your understanding.

@EstelleKershaw Hello Estelle,
could you please provide us with the booking reference/ticket number and e-mail address associated? For confidentiality reasons, we suggest you to send the details by private message.
